oaded frictional term, we are able to quantitatively\nexplain the experimental and simulation results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 May 2013 13:38:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Jun 2013 20:02:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-06"}
